The animations files are not too big to be loaded if you edit the correct methods. The header was not really changed at all. I have gotten the animations to load successfully and have been working on getting the 474 seq.dat ready to pack into the 317 client. No, I will not release how I did it, but I can tell you the header was not really changed for anims.

Just so you know:
Its only the new NPC’s that were added, that need the new animations. Or at least the ones I have used so far, don’t need them, except for some of the GWD NPC’s I have added.
